@deffn Function gnome-druid-page-edge-new-with-vals  (position@tie{}@code{<gnome-edge-position>}) (antialiased@tie{}@code{bool}) (title@tie{}@code{mchars}) (text@tie{}@code{mchars}) (logo@tie{}@code{<gdk-pixbuf>}) (watermark@tie{}@code{<gdk-pixbuf>}) (top_watermark@tie{}@code{<gdk-pixbuf>}) @result{}@tie{} (ret@tie{}@code{<gtk-widget>})
