acceptable for any of them to be @samp{@code{#f}}. Position should be
@samp{GNOME_EDGE_START}, @samp{GNOME_EDGE_FINISH} or @samp{GNOME_EDGE_OTHER}.

@table @var
@item position
Position in druid.

@item antialiased
Use an antialiased canvas

@item title
The title.

@item text
The introduction text.

@item logo
The logo in the upper right corner.

@item watermark
The watermark on the left.

@item top-watermark
The watermark on the left.

@item ret
@code{<gtk-widget>} pointer to a new @code{<gnome-druid-page-edge>}.

@end table

@end deffn

